fr.umlv.wallj.game

Interface Cell

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Empty, Garbage, Trashcan, Wall

    public interface Cell
    Represents a cell in the grid of a board. It can be either a Wall, a Garbage, a Trashcan, or an Empty cell. The four constants WALL, EMPTY, GARBAGE and TRASHCAN are the differents types of Cells. Each cells has x and y coordinates.
    Author:
    Severin Gosset - Denis Biguenet
